      **************************************                            00081800
       3000-I-LEER-CLI.                                                 00081902
                                                                        00082000
           READ CLIENTE  INTO WK-TBCLIE.                                00082102
                                                                        00082300
           EVALUATE WS-CLI-CODE                                         00082402

           WHEN '00'                                                    00082500
